            <div class="main-content">
                <section id="s-intro">
                    <h2>Welcome to Driven by STEM!</h2>
                    <p>Ready to race? This isn't just about speed—it's about smart engineering choices that make you faster, safer, and more efficient on the track.</p>
                    <p>In this game, you'll learn how real F1 engineers make decisions by testing different tradeoffs in your own race car.</p>
                </section>
                
                <section id="s-video">
                    <h2>📹 Watch How It Works</h2>
