                        • Highlight code-to-gameplay connection<br>
                        • YouTube embed or direct video player</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                
                <section id="s-do">
                    <h2>What You'll Do</h2>
                    <p>Jump into a fast-paced racing experience where you can:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>🏎️ Drive and test your car on the track</li>
                        <li>⚙️ Tune your car's speed, handling, and efficiency</li>
                        <li>🔬 See how each change affects your performance</li>
                        <li>🎯 Make smart tradeoffs between speed and control</li>
                        <li>💻 Change the code and watch what happens</li>
                        <li>🏆 Compare different strategies and find what works best</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <div class="notice">
                        <p><strong>[PLACEHOLDER: Screenshot gallery]</strong></p>
                        <p style="opacity: 0.7;">• 3-4 gameplay screenshots showing different stages<br>
                        • Code editor view with annotations<br>
                        • Before/after comparison images</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                
                <section id="s-learn">
                    <h2>What You'll Learn</h2>
                    <p>Through gameplay, you'll discover:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>How code changes create real results you can see and feel</li>
                        <li>Why engineers balance performance, safety, and sustainability</li>
                        <li>How to test ideas, learn from results, and improve your design</li>
                        <li>What careers in racing, software, and engineering look like</li>
                        <li>That the best solution isn't always the fastest one</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
                
                <section id="s-start">
                    <h2>How to Get Started</h2>
                    <div class="notice">
                        <p><strong>Follow the skillmap activities:</strong></p>
