                            <li>You'll build the game step by step using code blocks</li>
                            <li>Test your changes in the simulator right away</li>
                            <li>Complete each challenge to unlock the next one</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p style="margin-top: 1rem;"><strong>Ready to race?</strong></p>
                        <div class="cta-buttons" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                            <a href="https://arcade.makecode.com/--skillmap#github:asmeets/driven-by-stem/skillmap" class="btn primary">🎮 Start Playing</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                
                <section id="s-tips">
                    <h2>Tips for Success</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Don't worry about getting it perfect—testing and trying again is how engineers work!</li>
                        <li>Pay attention to how different values change the way your car handles</li>
                        <li>Think about real race cars: what matters more on different tracks?</li>
                        <li>Try extreme values to see what happens, then find the sweet spot</li>
                        <li>Share your discoveries with classmates and compare strategies</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
                
