                <section id="e-contributors">
                    <h2>For Contributors</h2>
                    <p>If you contribute to this project, keep changes:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Easy to teach:</strong> facilitators should be able to explain it in a minute or less</li>
                        <li><strong>Easy to remix:</strong> students should be able to change values and see clear results</li>
                        <li><strong>Easy to run:</strong> it should work reliably in a live classroom or activation setting</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>This project is meant to feel like a pit lane for ideas: test a change, watch what happens, and improve the next run.</p>
                    
                    <div class="notice">
                        <p><strong>[PLACEHOLDER: Technical documentation]</strong></p>
                        <p style="opacity: 0.7;">• Architecture overview<br>
                        • Code structure guide<br>
                        • Asset creation guidelines<br>
